{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, with n f = 30 by default, our improved implementation results in a 30-fold speed-up.",
    "Extensibility of CellRank 2.",
    "While we already provide multiple kernels tailored to different data modalities, current and future technologies provide additional sources of information.",
    "Concrete examples include spatially resolved time-course studies [59] [60] [61] and genetic lineage-tracing data [55] [56] [57] [58], previously already integrated in the CellRank 2 ecosystem 23, 24.",
    "Our modular interface makes CellRank 2 easily extensible toward (1) alternative single-cell data modalities by including new kernels and (2) alternative trajectory descriptions generating different hypotheses through new estimators."
